{"tid":240150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"匯豐銀行31歲副總裁涉收受利益　助批信貸申請","createTime":"2017-05-12T08:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T13:01:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e65fac59a966909c7cbf623314ff693da131a92","tid":240150,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"匯豐銀行有限公司副總裁涉於14至16年間接受代理人提供的利益，包括私家車、電子遊戲機、現金及咖啡機等，作出對代理人公司的信貸申請及維持該等信貸安排的誘因或報酬。副總裁及該代理人及後被廉政公署起訴6項代理人接受利益及向代理人提供利益罪，二人就控罪暫毋須答辯，案件押後至7月7日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n首被告副總裁梁肇倫（31歲）及次被告朱江（43歲）今於西九龍法院應訊，首被告與保安主管曾錦鳳（55歲）各另被控一項披露受調查人身份罪，案件一併押後待辯方索取法律意見後再訊。<br />\n法庭記者：梁銘姿"},{"pid":"4c6954f6c96d80c321ebb3dac991d669690e8805","tid":240150,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"副總裁距離CEO係咪差一級？"},{"pid":"114b296dddbdb9c306dbe0e6199ce1e564f443af","tid":240150,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2ec3e4f17f0bc47eb2872862046573fe98960d6","tid":240150,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82d1c98d9ff1f66b09836a8b89535b326bbd79f8","tid":240150,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>31歲點先做到副總裁？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae868769ab6515d16f6bc2791d7fb88c3d4b626c","tid":240150,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"叫番vp唔好譯仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdda5517cfaa37c20d12fe42e657a89038d1bdef","tid":240150,"uid":23235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫番vp唔好譯仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a